## Architecture

<!-- WHY: Show how components connect. A visual diagram is strongly recommended. -->
<!-- WHY: Explain data flow between components. -->

```
[User Input]
     │
     ▼
[{{ENTRY_COMPONENT}}] ─── {{ROUTING_CONDITION_1}} ──► [{{COMPONENT_A}}]
     │                                                        │
     └── {{ROUTING_CONDITION_2}} ──► [{{COMPONENT_B}}]       │
                                           │                  ▼
                                           └────────► [{{OUTPUT_COMPONENT}}] ──► [Deliverable]
```

**Data flow:**
1. User invokes system via `{{ENTRY_POINT}}`
2. `{{ENTRY_COMPONENT}}` routes to the appropriate component based on intent
3. `{{COMPONENT_A}}` handles `{{INTENT_A}}` and produces `{{OUTPUT_A}}`
4. `{{OUTPUT_COMPONENT}}` formats and delivers the final result

