## Quality Gate

<!-- WHY: D4 requires 3+ verifiable criteria before output delivery. -->
<!-- WHY: System-level gates focus on composition integrity, not just individual component output. -->

Before delivering system output, verify:
- [ ] All activated components produced output (no silent routing failures)
- [ ] Data contracts between components were honored (no schema mismatches)
- [ ] Routing decision was deterministic — ambiguous inputs triggered clarification, not guessing
- [ ] Shared knowledge base was read before any component wrote output
- [ ] Final output reflects synthesis from all activated components, not just the terminal one
